  "detailed_description": "<h1>ROAD MAP</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/8f59c7871b6aa108b68ba45573f2378b.avif?t=1765442239\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras_big/8f59c7871b6aa108b68ba45573f2378b.avif?t=1765442239 width=800 height=484 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/fed6b899b6985f4aefffe56cd92c48d1.poster.avif?t=1765442239\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/fed6b899b6985f4aefffe56cd92c48d1.webm?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/fed6b899b6985f4aefffe56cd92c48d1.mp4?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The hour of reckoning for sins has come. The Forgotten God brought down flames on the Earth. All living things died to start a new era. But... the last hero is alive. And he wants to stay alive in this new world, despite the fact that it’s not welcoming at all<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/e3b485f845ee33650e15c076b89e7336.poster.avif?t=1765442239\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/e3b485f845ee33650e15c076b89e7336.webm?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/e3b485f845ee33650e15c076b89e7336.mp4?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A variety of maps and horrible opponents<br></li><li>Impressive bosses<br></li><li>Lots of abilities and equipment<br></li><li>Various characters<br></li><li>Many hours of intense gameplay<br></li><li>The Mystery of the Last Survivor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/64e01ab7756d5314c7731b27ab491722.poster.avif?t=1765442239\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/64e01ab7756d5314c7731b27ab491722.webm?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250080/extras/64e01ab7756d5314c7731b27ab491722.mp4?t=1765442239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
